column5: Well it looks like instead of going for grouse on Wednesday my brother and I are going back for that musky that beat up that smallmouth.  This guy:   Did this:    So I'm going back with this:      Stay tuned.
Well if that Bondy bait doesn't work tomorrow, you can always save it for Lakers in 4 months or so!
Good luck can't wait to see that ski
go get her. ive been trying to get even with one since 1965
Good luck Rob.  I put an extra box of shells  in my pack, for the walk up the hill.   Have fun.
I would, if I had an ice rod that could handle it.
thats the spirit, show that nasty bully who's boss. May I suggest anything that resembles a smallmouth bass...other than a smallmouth bass itself
Great weather, kids dropped off, time for some fish.
Nail 'em Bondy style Rob!!!  That green puke Bondy bait sold at BPS might be a better rep of that beaten smallie though.  Even has the orange tail.
Got some bass on topwaters. Missed a few, one was big and had a musky follow. I'll put up some photos when I get them from my brother.
